          "value": "Why: dim2 gaai2"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "To ask 'why', use <strong>點解</strong> (dim2 gaai2). To answer, start your sentence with <strong>因為</strong> (jan1 wai6), which means 'because'."
        },
